<F P=100> INTERREGIONAL AFFAIRS </F>
<H3> <TI>   Further Reportage on CIS Leaders Summit 15 Apr </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Further Reportage on CIS Leaders Summit 15 Apr </PHRASE></F></HT>
<H4>    New CIS Economic Weekly Published </H4>

<F P=102> LD1504141994 Moscow ITAR-TASS in English 1052 GMT 15 Apr 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD1504141994 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow ITAR-TASS </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

<F P=106> [By Business-TASS] </F>
  [Text] Moscow April 15 TASS -- The first issue of a new 
economic weekly entitled "CIS: COMMON MARKET" was released on 
Friday timed to coincide with another CIS summit which opened in 
Moscow today. 
  The weekly was prepared with the assistance of the ITAR-TASS 
news agency. The aim of the new newspaper is to organise common 
information space in the economic sphere. 
  A decision to publish the weekly was adopted by heads of 
government of the 12 Commonwealth States in Ashgabat last 
December. 

</TEXT>

