<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Corruption Proceedings Against Rutskoy Reopened </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD1504165294 Moscow Radio Rossii Network in Russian 1600 GMT 
15 Apr 94 </F>

