<F P=104>  Moscow Radio Rossii Network </F>
<F P=105>  Russian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] ITAR-TASS has learned that Russia's procurator 
general has reopened the so-called Rutskoy trust case, in 
connection with the incompleteness of the investigation 
conducted earlier. Among other things, Rutskoy, the notary who 
verified the documents, and other persons were not questioned on 
all the circumstances of the trust agreement. Furthermore, a 
number of expert investigations need to be carried out, 
including one into the trust agreement itself. 

