<F P=102>   LD1804001094 Moscow Mayak Radio Network in Russian 2330 GMT 
17 Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD1804001094 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow Mayak Radio Network </F>
<F P=105>  Russian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] The participants in the All-Union Congress of the 
Union of Officers held in Moscow's suburbs have decided to ask 
the Russian military leadership to cancel the joint 
Russian-American military exercises planned for the summer of 
this year. The Union of Officers regards assisting and 
participating in the maneuvers as treason. The Congress passed 
a resolution assessing the recent air strikes against Bosnia as 
preparing a bridgehead for the mounting of aggression against 
Russia and other Slav states. In this connection the delegates 
demanded an immediate convocation of the UN Security Council to 
end the escalation of the violence and genocide of the Serbian 
people. This was reported by the Interfax agency. 

</TEXT>

