<F P=106> [By ITAR-TASS special correspondent Gennadiy Yezhov] </F>
  [Text] St. Petersburg, 17 Apr -- The coordination of 
international assistance for Russian reforms, particularly the 
problem of creating a multilateral agency to guarantee foreign 
investment against non-commercial risks -- this and other issues 
