<H3> <TI>   EBRD Credits for Satellite </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    EBRD Credits for Satellite </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD1704105794 Moscow ITAR-TASS in English 1044 GMT 17 Apr 94 </F>
