<H3> <TI>   Glazyev: Economic Situation Not Reassuring </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Glazyev: Economic Situation Not Reassuring </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   PM1804092194 Moscow ROSSIYSKAYA GAZETA in Russian 16 Apr 94 
First Edition p 3 </F>

