<F P=100> Regional Affairs </F>
<H3> <TI>   Yeltsin Edict on Construction of Ingush Capital </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Yeltsin Edict on Construction of Ingush Capital </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD1504192194 Moscow ITAR-TASS in English 1848 GMT 15 Apr 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD1504192194 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow ITAR-TASS </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

<F P=106> [By ITAR-TASS] </F>
  [Text] Moscow April 15 TASS--A decree of Russian President 
Boris Yeltsin on construction of the Ingush capital was signed 
here today. Follows the text of the decree: 
  "On Construction of the Capital of the Republic of 
Ingushetia. 
  "In order to assist the Ingush people in construction of the 
capital of the Ingush republic as a major attribute of its 
forming statehood and in accordance with the Russian 
Constitution and the Russian law `On Formation of the Ingush 
Republic Within the Russian Federation' I resolute: 
  "1. To support the initiative of republics, territories and 
regions of the Russian Federation on joint construction of the 
capital of the Ingush republic. 
  "2. To instruct the Russian Government to elaborate no 
later than June 1994 a set of arrangements to design and 
construct the capital of the Ingush Republic. 
  "3. This decree shall enter into force since the moment 
of its signing". 

</TEXT>

