  [Text] Afghanistan has accused Uzbekistan of supporting 
the opponent of the country's president, Borhanoddin Rabbani, 
that is Prime Minister Golboddin Hekmatyar, and his ally General 
Dustum -- an ethnic Uzbek whose troops also consist of Uzbeks. 
