intelligence leadership to the effect that Tashkent has given 
Dustum aircraft to bomb the Afghan capital and this week they 
have already struck against Kabul. Surat Mirkasymov, Uzbekistan 
charge d'affaires ad interim to India, has categorically denied 
the Afghan intelligence service's statement. 

