BFN 

<F P=106> [By ITAR-TASS correspondent Vladas Burbulis] </F>
  [Text] Vilnius April 15 TASS--A statement of Lithuanian 
Sejm opposition leader Vitautas Landsbergis on the Russian 
intention to join the Council of Europe and his accusations of 
"Moscow that allegedly commands the Lithuanian Foreign Ministry" 
was circulated in Strasbourg during a visit of Lithuanian 
