BFN 

  [Excerpt] Reports are coming in of new instances of 
arbitrary seizure of Black Sea Fleet property by the Ukrainian 
military. 
  According to river motorboat crews, a group of eight 
Ukrainian naval servicemen arrived in Izmail at 1300. They 
handed to the unit commander an order from the Ukrainian defense 
minister to the effect that the unit was disbanded and replaced 
by a third brigade to guard the Ukrainian naval military 
district. 
  Sources close to the Black Sea Fleet headquarters have 
learned that on 15 April, near the settlement of Perevalnaya, 
near Simferopol, one of the battalions of a mechanised division 
of the Ukrainian armed forces has been placed on full combat 
alert. Battalion personnel have been issued ammunition. Similar 
measures have been taken at an artillery unit of the same 
mechanised brigade. [passage omitted] 

