newspaper; in Kozyatyn E.D. No. 57, Nedvyha, a worker 
(democratically-oriented), defeated the Rukh candidate; in 
Nemyriv E.D. No. 58, Volodymyr Stratevych, senior scientific 
associate of the Institute of State and Law of the Academy of 
Sciences of Ukraine, defeated an official of the Security 
Service of Ukraine; in Pohrebyshche E.D. No. 59, Volodymyr 
