Kostyantyn Piskunovskyy, deputy to the former Supreme Council of 
Ukraine representing the "Party of Power," defeated Vasyl Kizka, 
correspondent of the newspaper Nezavisimost. 
  Runoff elections will be held in the remaining six electoral 
districts. 

