<F P=106> ["Election Results in Kiev"] </F>
  [Text] The winners in the three electoral districts of Kiev 
where people's deputies of Ukraine were elected on 10 April are: 
in Radyanskyy E.D. No. 16 -- Myroslav Horbatyuk, the Rukh 
candidate; in Svyatoshynskyy E.D. No. 18 -- Ivan Zayets (Rukh), 
a deputy to the old Supreme Council of Ukraine (he defeated a 
