Protection Minister Yuriy Kostenko, a Rukh member (he defeated 
Semen Yufa, chairman of the Merkuriy Cooperative Society). 
  No deputies were elected in five other districts [because 
neither candidate obtained the qualifying number of votes], and 
the elections in the remaining districts were invalid [because 
voter turnout was lower than required by law]. 

