<HEADER>
<AU>   FBIS-SOV-94-074 </AU>
Daily Report 
<DATE1>  14 Apr 1994 </DATE1>

</HEADER>

<F P=100> National Affairs </F>
<H3> <TI>   Presidential Edict Appoints New Deputy Defense Minister </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Presidential Edict Appoints New Deputy Defense Minister </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   AU1504123194 Kiev DEMOKRATYCHNA UKRAYINA in Ukrainian 14 Apr 
94 p 1 </F>

<F P=103> AU1504123194 </F>
<F P=104>  Kiev DEMOKRATYCHNA UKRAYINA </F>
<F P=105>  Ukrainian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

<F P=106> [Unattributed report: "The Minister of Defense Has a New </F>
Deputy"] 
