General Vasyl Tymofiyovych Sabkov as Ukraine's deputy minister 
of defense. He is also commander of Ukraine's Armed Forces 
Ground Troops commander. Previously, Vasyl Tymofiyovych headed 
the Ciscarpathian Military District. 

