<F P=100> RUSSIA NATIONAL AFFAIRS </F>
<F P=101> Political Issues </F>
<H3> <TI>   Yeltsin Establishes Presidential Group of Experts </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Yeltsin Establishes Presidential Group of Experts </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD1604141094 Moscow Mayak Radio Network in Russian 1300 GMT 
16 Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD1604141094 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow Mayak Radio Network </F>
<F P=105>  Russian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Boris Yeltsin has decided to set up a group of 
experts under the Russian president. An edict signed by him 
says the group will consist of eight people. Their names have 
not been given. Among other things, the experts will draft 
proposals regarding the implementation of the president's 
decisions in the economic sphere. They will also compile 
speeches for him, as well as analytical and information memos. 

</TEXT>

