<F P=100> Latvia </F>
<H3> <TI>   Sweden to Send Financial Aid to Develop Baltic Defenses </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Sweden to Send Financial Aid to Develop Baltic Defenses </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD1804172694 Riga Radio Riga Network in Latvian 0900 GMT 18 
Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD1804172694 </F>
<F P=104>  Riga Radio Riga Network </F>
<F P=105>  Latvian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] The Swedish Government has decided to grant 1.4 
million Swedish krona to create defense systems in the Baltic 
states. These funds will be used for consultations and 
training, and the acquisition of equipment and radars for both 
land and sea border protection. 
  Experts from the Swedish defense forces have already become 
acquainted with the Baltic states' defense systems and have 
worked out proposals on how to improve them. 

</TEXT>

