<F P=100> Azerbaijan </F>
<H3> <TI>   Armenian Attacks in Northern Karabakh Said Repulsed </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Armenian Attacks in Northern Karabakh Said Repulsed </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   NC1804174394 Baku Azerbaycan Radio Televiziyasi Television 
Network in Azeri 1600 GMT 18 Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> NC1804174394 </F>
<F P=104>  Baku Azerbaycan Radio Televiziyasi Television 
Network </F>

<F P=105>  Azeri </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

<F P=106> ["Defense Ministry Press Service report" -- read by </F>
announcer] 
  [Text] Having reinforced its troops in northern Karabakh 
and with the support of a number of tanks, the Armenian Armed 
Forces launched attacks towards Terter on the afternoon of 17 
April. Armenian units resumed their tank attack last night and 
in the early hours of 18 April; infantry troops also joined the 
fight. Bloody battles continued until 0800. 
  The enemy's attacks were repelled, and they were driven back 
to their initial positions. Five tanks and one infantry 
fighting vehicle were destroyed and nearly 90 Armenian troops 
were killed. 

</TEXT>

