<H3> <TI>   Clashes Reported on Border With Afghanistan </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Clashes Reported on Border With Afghanistan </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   PM1804110194 Moscow ROSSIYSKAYA GAZETA in Russian 16 Apr 94 
First Edition p 6 </F>

<F P=103> PM1804110194 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow ROSSIYSKAYA GAZETA </F>
<F P=105>  Russian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

<F P=106> [Report from roundup of ROSSIYSKAYA GAZETA and ITAR-TASS </F>
reports: "Unsettled on Border Again"] 
  [Text] Attempts by armed groups to penetrate Tajikistan's 
territory are not ceasing. 
  Over the past 24 hours on the sector of the Pyandzh 
detachment's 10th border post a large bandit formation tried to 
break through from Afghanistan onto the Republic's territory but 
when it met with resistance was obliged to retreat. Fighting 
also broke out on the sector of the Moskovskiy border guards 
detachment's 12th border post where heavy weapons had to be 
used. There were no casualties on the border guards' side. 

</TEXT>

