  [Text] Dushanbe 16 April, TASS -- The head of the Tajik 
Parliament, Emomali Rakhmonov has estimated the results of the 
Moscow summit of the CIS countries as evidence of the 
strengthening of mutual understanding of the countries of the 
Commonwealth that has entered the "strongest period of its 
