  In an exclusive interview with TIA "KHOVAR" on Saturday he 
noted the Commonwealth of Independent States is moving along the 
road of the realization of the idea of establishing a real 
economic union and drawing up a mechanism of its functioning. 
During the discussion of economic and political issues the 
meeting showed considerable mutual understanding between heads 
of CIS countries, said Rakhmonov. 

