<F P=101> International Affairs </F>
<H3> <TI>   Swede Expelled for Seeking Nuclear Warhead Components </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Swede Expelled for Seeking Nuclear Warhead Components </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD1604082694 Kiev UNIAN in Ukrainian 2005 GMT 15 Apr 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD1604082694 </F>
<F P=104>  Kiev UNIAN </F>
<F P=105>  Ukrainian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] On 15 April the press center of the Security 
Service of Ukraine reported that Swedish subject, Erik Olaf 
Estenson, born in 1962, who was temporarily staying on the 
territory of our state, was expelled from Ukraine for attempts 
to carry out actions that can be qualified as international 
nuclear terrorism in relation to a foreign state. 
  As UNIAN learned from reliable sources, the Swedish subject 
was seeking contacts with relevant specialists with the aim of 
taking nuclear warhead components away from Ukraine. According 
to unofficial data, the organization which, presumably, tasked 
Estensson has not yet been disclosed. 

</TEXT>

