<H3> <TI>   Ingush Diet Asks Yeltsin To Impose Direct Federal Rule </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Ingush Diet Asks Yeltsin To Impose Direct Federal Rule </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   MK1904075094 Moscow SEGODNYA in Russian 19 Apr 94 p 2 </F>
<F P=103> MK1904075094 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow SEGODNYA </F>
<F P=105>  Russian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

<F P=106> [Report by Natalya Gorodetskaya under the "Caucasus" rubric: </F>
"Ingushetia Urges Introduction of Federal Rule in State of 
Emergency Zone"] 
  [Excerpt] [Passage omitted] Ingushetia's parliament 
yesterday discussed the situation in the state of emergency zone 
and passed a decree "On the Situation in the Zone Affected by 
the State of Emergency on North Ossetia and Ingushetia 
Territories and Measures to Uphold Citizens' Rights." The 
decree says that while Russian Federation laws do not work in 
the state of emergency zone, the rights of Russian citizens are 
being trampled, and the Provisional Administration has shown 
that it is completely incapable of stabilizing the situation. 
Ingushetia's parliament sees the suspension of local bodies of 
power of North Ossetia in Prigorodnyy Rayon and the introduction 
of direct federal rule on this territory as the only way out of 
the crisis. Ingushetia's parliament has forwarded to the 
Russian Federation president a special statement to this effect. 
[passage omitted] 

</TEXT>

