<F P=106> [Announcer-read report; from the "Aty-Baty" program] </F>
  [Text] Leaflets appeared in the city of Murmansk-150, 
which is the home for the first submarine flotilla of the 
Northern Fleet. They call on officers and warrant officers to 
carry out a joint protest act against the delays of pay and 
unsatisfactory supply of clothing and related gear. The 
leaflets propose to block the road leading from living quarters 
to the submarine base. 

