<H3> <TI>   Commissions Approved </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Commissions Approved </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   AU1904084294 Tbilisi SVOBODNAYA GRUZIYA in Russian 8 Apr 94 
p 3 </F>

<F P=103> AU1904084294 </F>
<F P=104>  Tbilisi SVOBODNAYA GRUZIYA </F>
<F P=105>  Russian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

<F P=106> ["Directive" issued by Givi Lominadze, Republic of Georgia </F>
state minister, chairman of the Interim Committee for Emergency 
Situations in Western Georgia] 
  [Text] 1. To approve the Statute on Temporary Commissions 
for Reconciliation With Supporters of the Ex-President Attached 
to Bodies of Local Administration for Emergency Situations in 
Western Georgia that has been submitted. 
  2. The statute comes into force on the day of its 
publication. 
  3. To entrust bodies of local administration with forming 
these commissions before 10 March and submitting information on 
the composition of the commission to the Temporary Committee for 
Emergency Situations. 
  [Signed] G. Lominadze, Republic of Georgia state 
minister, chairman of the Interim Committee for Emergency 
Situations in western Georgia. 

</TEXT>

